main event: High speed track observed on ground radar by 3 USAF operators at Mt. Laguna.
interesting points: The speed of the track was estimated at 1,143 knots, Various speeds were calculated, showing discrepancies between radar readings, The object could possibly be a test vehicle from Hughes, The radar showed no internal interference during the sighting, The duration of the tracking was 62 seconds.
witness description: USAF operators, including radar technicians and control technicians
